### Payment Service API Test Requests

### Direct Service Access (Development)
### 1. Create Payment Intent
POST http://localhost:8084/payments/intents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user_123",
  "amount": 29.99,
  "currency": "USD",
  "provider": "STRIPE",
  "description": "Test payment for order #12345",
  "metadata": {
    "order_id": "12345",
    "product_type": "subscription"
  }
}

### 2. Create Payment Intent (EUR)
POST http://localhost:8084/payments/intents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user_456",
  "amount": 49.99,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "provider": "STRIPE",
  "description": "Premium subscription payment",
  "metadata": {
    "subscription_type": "premium",
    "billing_cycle": "monthly"
  }
}

### 3. Get Payment Intent Details
GET http://localhost:8084/payments/intents/pi_test_1234567890

### 4. Create Payment Intent (Invalid - Missing Amount)
POST http://localhost:8084/payments/intents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user_789",
  "currency": "USD",
  "provider": "STRIPE",
  "description": "Invalid payment request"
}

### 5. Create Payment Intent (Invalid - Negative Amount)
POST http://localhost:8084/payments/intents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user_999",
  "amount": -10.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "provider": "STRIPE",
  "description": "Invalid negative amount"
}

### 6. Create Payment Intent (Invalid - Wrong Currency Format)
POST http://localhost:8084/payments/intents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user_888",
  "amount": 25.00,
  "currency": "USDD",
  "provider": "STRIPE",
  "description": "Invalid currency format"
}

### Gateway Access (Production)
### 7. Create Payment Intent via Gateway
POST http://localhost:8085/api/v1/payments/intents
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token_here

{
  "userId": "user_123",
  "amount": 29.99,
  "currency": "USD",
  "provider": "STRIPE",
  "description": "Payment via gateway"
}

### 8. Get Payment Intent via Gateway
GET http://localhost:8085/api/v1/payments/intents/pi_test_1234567890
Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token_here

